                    <article id="post-6026" class="kb-article-excerpt post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail">
        <header class="entry-header page-header">
            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="../../../post/6026.html" rel="bookmark">[ Laravel 5.3 文档 ] 综合话题 —— 事件广播</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2016-09-18T14:57:33+08:00">2016-09-18</time>
                    <time class="updated" datetime="2016-09-18T14:58:21+08:00">2016-09-18 14:58:21</time>
                </span>
                <span class="byline"> by
                    <span class="author vcard">
                        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></i>
                        <a class="url fn n" href="../../../author/nonfu">
                            学院君
                        </a>
                    </span>
                </span>
                <span class="article-views">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-eye"></i>
                    12438 Views
                </span>
                <span class="comments-link">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-bubbles2"></i>
                    <a href="../../../post/6026.html#comments">
                        13 Comments
                    </a>
                </span>
            </div><!-- .entry-meta -->
        </header><!-- .entry-header -->

        <div class="clearfix"></div>

                                                                                                    <div class="pull-left kb-thumb-medium hidden-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../../../post/6026.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="256" height="128" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/laravel-256x128.jpg" class="img-rounded wp-post-image" alt=""/>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                                                                                <div class="kb-thumb-large visible-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../../../post/6026.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="640" height="200" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/laravel-640x200.jpg" class="img wp-post-image" alt="" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                    
        <div class="entry entry-excerpt">
            <p>1、简介
在很多现代 Web 应用中，Web 套接字（WebSockets）被用于实现实时更新的用户接口。当一些数据在服务器上被更新，通常一条消息通过 websocket 连接被发送给客户端处理。这为我们提供了一个更强大的、更有效的选择来持续拉取应用的更新。

为帮助你构建这样的应用，Laravel 让通过 websocket 连接广播事件变得简单。广播 Laravel 事件允许你...</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clearfix"></div>
