    <article id="post-6009" class="kb-article-excerpt post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail">
        <header class="entry-header page-header">
            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="../../../post/6009.html" rel="bookmark">[ Laravel 5.3 文档 ] 安全 —— 哈希（Hashing）</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2016-09-16T22:54:57+08:00">2016-09-16</time>
                    <time class="updated" datetime="2016-09-16T22:54:57+08:00">2016-09-16 22:54:57</time>
                </span>
                <span class="byline"> by
                    <span class="author vcard">
                        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></i>
                        <a class="url fn n" href="../../../author/nonfu">
                            学院君
                        </a>
                    </span>
                </span>
                <span class="article-views">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-eye"></i>
                    6429 Views
                </span>
                <span class="comments-link">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-bubbles2"></i>
                    <a href="../../../post/6009.html#comments">
                        1 Comments
                    </a>
                </span>
            </div><!-- .entry-meta -->
        </header><!-- .entry-header -->

        <div class="clearfix"></div>

                                                                                                    <div class="pull-left kb-thumb-medium hidden-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../../../post/6009.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="256" height="128" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/laravel-256x128.jpg" class="img-rounded wp-post-image" alt=""/>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                                                                                <div class="kb-thumb-large visible-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../../../post/6009.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="640" height="200" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/laravel-640x200.jpg" class="img wp-post-image" alt="" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                    
        <div class="entry entry-excerpt">
            <p>1、简介
Laravel 的 Hash 门面为存储用户密码提供了安全的 Bcrypt 哈希算法。如果你正在使用 Laravel 应用自带的LoginController和RegisterController控制器，它们将会自动在注册和认证时使用该 Bcrypt。
注：Bcrypt 是散列密码的绝佳选择，因为其“工作因子”是可调整的，这意味着随着硬件功能的提升，生成哈希所花费的时间也会...</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <footer class="entry-meta">
            <p class="visible-xs">
                <a rel="bookmark" href="../../../post/6009.html" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-link"></i> 阅读全文
                </a>
            </p>
            <p class="pull-right hidden-xs">
                <a rel="bookmark" href="../../../post/6009.html" class="btn btn-primary">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-link"></i> 阅读全文
                </a>
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted hidden-xs meta-data">
                <span class="cat-links">
					<i class="glyphicon glyphicon-folder-open"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                    分类：
                    <a href="../../../docs/laravel-5_3" rel="category tag">
                        Laravel 5.3
                    </a>
                </span>

