    <article id="post-6002" class="kb-article-excerpt post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail">
        <header class="entry-header page-header">
            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="../../../post/6002.html" rel="bookmark">[ Laravel 5.3 文档 ] 安全 —— 加密</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2016-09-15T08:58:24+08:00">2016-09-15</time>
                    <time class="updated" datetime="2016-09-15T08:58:24+08:00">2016-09-15 08:58:24</time>
                </span>
                <span class="byline"> by
                    <span class="author vcard">
                        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></i>
                        <a class="url fn n" href="../../../author/nonfu">
                            学院君
                        </a>
                    </span>
                </span>
                <span class="article-views">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-eye"></i>
                    6021 Views
                </span>
                <span class="comments-link">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-bubbles2"></i>
                    <a href="../../../post/6002.html#comments">
                        2 Comments
                    </a>
                </span>
            </div><!-- .entry-meta -->
        </header><!-- .entry-header -->

        <div class="clearfix"></div>

                                                                                                    <div class="pull-left kb-thumb-medium hidden-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../../../post/6002.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="256" height="128" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/laravel-256x128.jpg" class="img-rounded wp-post-image" alt=""/>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                                                                                <div class="kb-thumb-large visible-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../../../post/6002.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="640" height="200" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/laravel-640x200.jpg" class="img wp-post-image" alt="" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                    
        <div class="entry entry-excerpt">
            <p>1、简介
Laravel的加密器使用OpenSSL来提供AES-256和AES-128加密。强烈建议使用Laravel自带的加密设置，不要尝试推出自己“土生土长”的加密算法。所有Laravel加密过的值都使用消息授权码（MAC）进行签名以便底层值一经加密就不能修改。
2、配置
在使用Laravel的加密器之前，必须在配置文件config/app.php中设置key选项为32位随机字...</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clearfix"></div>
