    <article id="post-5978" class="kb-article-excerpt post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail">
        <header class="entry-header page-header">
            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="../../../post/5978.html" rel="bookmark">[ Laravel 5.3 文档 ] 安全 —— 用户授权</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2016-09-12T23:04:20+08:00">2016-09-12</time>
                    <time class="updated" datetime="2016-09-14T00:32:35+08:00">2016-09-14 00:32:35</time>
                </span>
                <span class="byline"> by
                    <span class="author vcard">
                        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></i>
                        <a class="url fn n" href="../../../author/nonfu">
                            学院君
                        </a>
                    </span>
                </span>
                <span class="article-views">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-eye"></i>
                    11173 Views
                </span>
                <span class="comments-link">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-bubbles2"></i>
                    <a href="../../../post/5978.html#comments">
                        4 Comments
                    </a>
                </span>
            </div><!-- .entry-meta -->
        </header><!-- .entry-header -->

        <div class="clearfix"></div>

                                                                                                    <div class="pull-left kb-thumb-medium hidden-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../../../post/5978.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="256" height="128" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/laravel-256x128.jpg" class="img-rounded wp-post-image" alt=""/>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                                                                                <div class="kb-thumb-large visible-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../../../post/5978.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="640" height="200" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/laravel-640x200.jpg" class="img wp-post-image" alt="" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                    
        <div class="entry entry-excerpt">
            <p>1、简介
除了提供开箱即用的认证服务之外，Laravel 还提供了一个简单的方式来管理授权逻辑以便控制对资源的访问权限。和认证一样，在Laravel中实现授权很简单，主要有两种方式：gates和policies。

可以将gates和policies分别看作路由和控制器，gates提供了简单的基于闭包的方式进行授权，而policies和控制器一样，对特定模型或资源上的复杂授权逻辑进...</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clearfix"></div>
